file_content.text: Should have this transport up and running in no time, thanks to you.
Selia Antares? I have the deactivation codes you need.
Finally! Been busting my hump trying to figure out a way to disarm this thing.
Wasn't sure C6-N8 would find someone. Sometimes rubs people the wrong way.
Thanks for all your help. Now I gotta punch in these deactivation codes so we can get this bird back in the air.
Your protocol droid told me you needed help.
Yeah? Well if you ain't got the deactivation codes from House Thul, you ain't helping.
